#. <section class="sutta" id="sn54.8"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn54.8:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 54"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 54"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn54.8:0.2"
msgid "1. Ekadhammavagga"
msgstr "1. One Thing"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 8. Padīpopamasutta → dīpasuttaṃ (bj) | dīpo (pts1)
msgctxt "sn54.8:0.3"
msgid "8. Padīpopamasutta"
msgstr "8. The Simile of the Lamp"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.8:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Ānāpānassatisamādhi, bhikkhave, bhāvito bahulīkato mahapphalo hoti "
"mahānisaṃso."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, when immersion due to mindfulness of breathing is developed and "
"cultivated it’s very fruitful and beneficial."

msgctxt "sn54.8:1.2"
msgid ""
"Kathaṃ bhāvito ca, bhikkhave, ānāpānassatisamādhi kathaṃ bahulīkato "
"mahapphalo hoti mahānisaṃso?"
msgstr "How so?"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.317"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.8:2.1"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu araññagato vā rukkhamūlagato vā suññāgāragato vā "
"nisīdati pallaṅkaṃ ābhujitvā ujuṃ kāyaṃ paṇidhāya parimukhaṃ satiṃ "
"upaṭṭhapetvā."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant has gone to a wilderness, or to the root of a tree, or "
"to an empty hut. They sit down cross-legged, with their body straight, and "
"establish mindfulness right there."

msgctxt "sn54.8:2.2"
msgid "So satova assasati, satova passasati."
msgstr "Just mindful, they breathe in. Mindful, they breathe out."

msgctxt "sn54.8:2.3"
msgid "Dīghaṃ vā assasanto ‘dīghaṃ assasāmī’ti pajānāti … pe …"
msgstr ""
"When breathing in heavily they know: ‘I’m breathing in heavily.’ When "
"breathing out heavily they know: ‘I’m breathing out heavily.’ …"

msgctxt "sn54.8:2.4"
msgid ""
"‘paṭinissaggānupassī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘paṭinissaggānupassī "
"passasissāmī’ti sikkhati."
msgstr ""
"They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe in observing letting go.’ They "
"practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe out observing letting go.’"

msgctxt "sn54.8:2.5"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ bhāvito kho, bhikkhave, ānāpānassatisamādhi evaṃ bahulīkato mahapphalo "
"hoti mahānisaṃso."
msgstr ""
"That’s how immersion due to mindfulness of breathing, when developed and "
"cultivated, is very fruitful and beneficial."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.8:3.1"
msgid ""
"Ahampi sudaṃ, bhikkhave, pubbeva sambodhā anabhisambuddho bodhisattova "
"samāno iminā vihārena bahulaṃ viharāmi."
msgstr ""
"Before my awakening—when I was still unawakened but intent on awakening—I "
"too usually practiced this kind of meditation."

msgctxt "sn54.8:3.2"
msgid ""
"Tassa mayhaṃ, bhikkhave, iminā vihārena bahulaṃ viharato neva kāyo kilamati "
"na cakkhūni;"
msgstr ""
"And while I was usually practicing this kind of meditation neither my body "
"nor my eyes became fatigued."

msgctxt "sn54.8:3.3"
msgid "anupādāya ca me āsavehi cittaṃ vimucci."
msgstr "And my mind was freed from defilements by not grasping."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.8:4.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu cepi ākaṅkheyya:"
msgstr "Now, a mendicant might wish:"

msgctxt "sn54.8:4.2"
msgid ""
"‘neva me kāyo kilameyya na cakkhūni, anupādāya ca me āsavehi cittaṃ "
"vimucceyyā’ti, "
msgstr ""
"‘May neither my body nor my eyes became fatigued. And may my mind be freed "
"from grasping without defilements.’ "

msgctxt "sn54.8:4.3"
msgid "ayameva ānāpānassatisamādhi sādhukaṃ manasi kātabbo."
msgstr ""
"So let them closely focus on this immersion due to mindfulness of breathing."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.8:5.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu cepi ākaṅkheyya:"
msgstr "Now, a mendicant might wish:"

msgctxt "sn54.8:5.2"
msgid "‘ye me gehasitā sarasaṅkappā te pahīyeyyun’ti, "
msgstr "‘May I give up memories and thoughts of the lay life.’ "

msgctxt "sn54.8:5.3"
msgid "ayameva ānāpānassatisamādhi sādhukaṃ manasi kātabbo."
msgstr ""
"So let them closely focus on this immersion due to mindfulness of breathing."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.8:6.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu cepi ākaṅkheyya:"
msgstr "Now, a mendicant might wish:"

msgctxt "sn54.8:6.2"
msgid "‘appaṭikūle paṭikūlasaññī vihareyyan’ti, "
msgstr "‘May I meditate perceiving the repulsive in the unrepulsive.’ "

msgctxt "sn54.8:6.3"
msgid "ayameva ānāpānassatisamādhi sādhukaṃ manasi kātabbo."
msgstr ""
"So let them closely focus on this immersion due to mindfulness of breathing."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.8:7.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu cepi ākaṅkheyya:"
msgstr "Now, a mendicant might wish:"

msgctxt "sn54.8:7.2"
msgid "‘paṭikūle appaṭikūlasaññī vihareyyan’ti, "
msgstr "‘May I meditate perceiving the unrepulsive in the repulsive.’ "

msgctxt "sn54.8:7.3"
msgid "ayameva ānāpānassatisamādhi sādhukaṃ manasi kātabbo."
msgstr ""
"So let them closely focus on this immersion due to mindfulness of breathing."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.8:8.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu cepi ākaṅkheyya:"
msgstr "Now, a mendicant might wish:"

msgctxt "sn54.8:8.2"
msgid "‘paṭikūle ca appaṭikūle ca paṭikūlasaññī vihareyyan’ti, "
msgstr ""
"‘May I meditate perceiving the repulsive in the unrepulsive and the "
"repulsive.’ "

msgctxt "sn54.8:8.3"
msgid "ayameva ānāpānassatisamādhi sādhukaṃ manasi kātabbo."
msgstr ""
"So let them closely focus on this immersion due to mindfulness of breathing."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.318"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.8:9.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu cepi ākaṅkheyya:"
msgstr "Now, a mendicant might wish:"

msgctxt "sn54.8:9.2"
msgid "‘paṭikūle ca appaṭikūle ca appaṭikūlasaññī vihareyyan’ti, "
msgstr ""
"‘May I meditate perceiving the unrepulsive in the repulsive and the "
"unrepulsive.’ "

msgctxt "sn54.8:9.3"
msgid "ayameva ānāpānassatisamādhi sādhukaṃ manasi kātabbo."
msgstr ""
"So let them closely focus on this immersion due to mindfulness of breathing."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.8:10.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu cepi ākaṅkheyya:"
msgstr "Now, a mendicant might wish:"

msgctxt "sn54.8:10.2"
msgid ""
"‘appaṭikūlañca paṭikūlañca tadubhayaṃ abhinivajjetvā upekkhako vihareyyaṃ "
"sato sampajāno’ti, "
msgstr ""
"‘May I meditate staying equanimous, mindful and aware, rejecting both the "
"repulsive and the unrepulsive.’ "

msgctxt "sn54.8:10.3"
msgid "ayameva ānāpānassatisamādhi sādhukaṃ manasi kātabbo."
msgstr ""
"So let them closely focus on this immersion due to mindfulness of breathing."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.8:11.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu cepi ākaṅkheyya:"
msgstr "Now, a mendicant might wish:"

msgctxt "sn54.8:11.2"
msgid ""
"‘vivicceva kāmehi vivicca akusalehi dhammehi savitakkaṃ savicāraṃ vivekajaṃ "
"pītisukhaṃ paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja vihareyyan’ti, "
msgstr ""
"‘Quite secluded from sensual pleasures, secluded from unskillful qualities, "
"may I enter and remain in the first absorption, which has the rapture and "
"bliss born of seclusion, while placing the mind and keeping it connected.’ "

msgctxt "sn54.8:11.3"
msgid "ayameva ānāpānassatisamādhi sādhukaṃ manasi kātabbo."
msgstr ""
"So let them closely focus on this immersion due to mindfulness of breathing."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.8:12.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu cepi ākaṅkheyya:"
msgstr "Now, a mendicant might wish:"

msgctxt "sn54.8:12.2"
msgid ""
"‘vitakkavicārānaṃ vūpasamā ajjhattaṃ sampasādanaṃ cetaso ekodibhāvaṃ "
"avitakkaṃ avicāraṃ samādhijaṃ pītisukhaṃ dutiyaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja "
"vihareyyan’ti, "
msgstr ""
"‘As the placing of the mind and keeping it connected are stilled, may I "
"enter and remain in the second absorption, which has the rapture and bliss "
"born of immersion, with internal clarity and confidence, and unified mind, "
"without placing the mind and keeping it connected.’ "

msgctxt "sn54.8:12.3"
msgid "ayameva ānāpānassatisamādhi sādhukaṃ manasi kātabbo."
msgstr ""
"So let them closely focus on this immersion due to mindfulness of breathing."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.8:13.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu cepi ākaṅkheyya:"
msgstr "Now, a mendicant might wish:"

msgctxt "sn54.8:13.2"
msgid ""
"‘pītiyā ca virāgā upekkhako ca vihareyyaṃ sato ca sampajāno, sukhañca kāyena "
"paṭisaṃvedeyyaṃ, yaṃ taṃ ariyā ācikkhanti—upekkhako satimā sukhavihārīti "
"tatiyaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja vihareyyan’ti, "
msgstr ""
"‘With the fading away of rapture, may I enter and remain in the third "
"absorption, where I will meditate with equanimity, mindful and aware, "
"personally experiencing the bliss of which the noble ones declare, “"
"Equanimous and mindful, one meditates in bliss.”’ "

msgctxt "sn54.8:13.3"
msgid "ayameva ānāpānassatisamādhi sādhukaṃ manasi kātabbo."
msgstr ""
"So let them closely focus on this immersion due to mindfulness of breathing."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc14"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.8:14.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu cepi ākaṅkheyya:"
msgstr "Now, a mendicant might wish:"

msgctxt "sn54.8:14.2"
msgid ""
"‘sukhassa ca pahānā dukkhassa ca pahānā pubbeva somanassadomanassānaṃ "
"atthaṅgamā adukkhamasukhaṃ upekkhāsatipārisuddhiṃ catutthaṃ jhānaṃ "
"upasampajja vihareyyan’ti, "
msgstr ""
"‘With the giving up of pleasure and pain, and the ending of former happiness "
"and sadness, may I enter and remain in the fourth absorption, without "
"pleasure or pain, with pure equanimity and mindfulness.’ "

msgctxt "sn54.8:14.3"
msgid "ayameva ānāpānassatisamādhi sādhukaṃ manasi kātabbo."
msgstr ""
"So let them closely focus on this immersion due to mindfulness of breathing."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc15"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.8:15.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu cepi ākaṅkheyya:"
msgstr "Now, a mendicant might wish:"

msgctxt "sn54.8:15.2"
msgid ""
"‘sabbaso rūpasaññānaṃ samatikkamā paṭighasaññānaṃ atthaṅgamā nānattasaññānaṃ "
"amanasikārā ananto ākāsoti ākāsānañcāyatanaṃ upasampajja vihareyyan’ti, "
msgstr ""
"‘Going totally beyond perceptions of form, with the ending of perceptions of "
"impingement, not focusing on perceptions of diversity, aware that “space is "
"infinite”, may I enter and remain in the dimension of infinite space.’ "

msgctxt "sn54.8:15.3"
msgid "ayameva ānāpānassatisamādhi sādhukaṃ manasi kātabbo."
msgstr ""
"So let them closely focus on this immersion due to mindfulness of breathing."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.319"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc16"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.8:16.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu cepi ākaṅkheyya:"
msgstr "Now, a mendicant might wish:"

msgctxt "sn54.8:16.2"
msgid ""
"‘sabbaso ākāsānañcāyatanaṃ samatikkamma anantaṃ viññāṇanti viññāṇañcāyatanaṃ "
"upasampajja vihareyyan’ti, "
msgstr ""
"‘Going totally beyond the dimension of infinite space, aware that “"
"consciousness is infinite”, may I enter and remain in the dimension of "
"infinite consciousness.’ "

msgctxt "sn54.8:16.3"
msgid "ayameva ānāpānassatisamādhi sādhukaṃ manasi kātabbo."
msgstr ""
"So let them closely focus on this immersion due to mindfulness of breathing."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc17"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.8:17.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu cepi ākaṅkheyya:"
msgstr "Now, a mendicant might wish:"

msgctxt "sn54.8:17.2"
msgid ""
"‘sabbaso viññāṇañcāyatanaṃ samatikkamma natthi kiñcīti ākiñcaññāyatanaṃ "
"upasampajja vihareyyan’ti, "
msgstr ""
"‘Going totally beyond the dimension of infinite consciousness, aware that “"
"there is nothing at all”, may I enter and remain in the dimension of "
"nothingness.’ "

msgctxt "sn54.8:17.3"
msgid "ayameva ānāpānassatisamādhi sādhukaṃ manasi kātabbo."
msgstr ""
"So let them closely focus on this immersion due to mindfulness of breathing."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc18"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.8:18.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu cepi ākaṅkheyya:"
msgstr "Now, a mendicant might wish:"

msgctxt "sn54.8:18.2"
msgid ""
"‘sabbaso ākiñcaññāyatanaṃ samatikkamma nevasaññānāsaññāyatanaṃ upasampajja "
"vihareyyan’ti, "
msgstr ""
"‘Going totally beyond the dimension of nothingness, may I enter and remain "
"in the dimension of neither perception nor non-perception.’ "

msgctxt "sn54.8:18.3"
msgid "ayameva ānāpānassatisamādhi sādhukaṃ manasi kātabbo."
msgstr ""
"So let them closely focus on this immersion due to mindfulness of breathing."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc19"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.8:19.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu cepi ākaṅkheyya:"
msgstr "Now, a mendicant might wish:"

msgctxt "sn54.8:19.2"
msgid ""
"‘sabbaso nevasaññānāsaññāyatanaṃ samatikkamma saññāvedayitanirodhaṃ "
"upasampajja vihareyyan’ti, "
msgstr ""
"‘Going totally beyond the dimension of neither perception nor non-"
"perception, may I enter and remain in the cessation of perception and "
"feeling.’ "

msgctxt "sn54.8:19.3"
msgid "ayameva ānāpānassatisamādhi sādhukaṃ manasi kātabbo."
msgstr ""
"So let them closely focus on this immersion due to mindfulness of breathing."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc20"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.8:20.1"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ bhāvite kho, bhikkhave, ānāpānassatisamādhimhi evaṃ bahulīkate, "
"sukhañce vedanaṃ vedayati, sā ‘aniccā’ti pajānāti, ‘anajjhositā’ti pajānāti, "
"‘anabhinanditā’ti pajānāti;"
msgstr ""
"When mindfulness of breathing has been developed and cultivated in this way, "
"if they feel a pleasant feeling, they understand that it’s impermanent, that "
"they’re not attached to it, and that they don’t take pleasure in it."

msgctxt "sn54.8:20.2"
msgid ""
"dukkhañce vedanaṃ vedayati, sā ‘aniccā’ti pajānāti, ‘anajjhositā’ti "
"pajānāti, ‘anabhinanditā’ti pajānāti;"
msgstr ""
"If they feel a painful feeling, they understand that it’s impermanent, that "
"they’re not attached to it, and that they don’t take pleasure in it."

msgctxt "sn54.8:20.3"
msgid ""
"adukkhamasukhañce vedanaṃ vedayati, ‘sā aniccā’ti pajānāti, ‘anajjhositā’ti "
"pajānāti, ‘anabhinanditā’ti pajānāti."
msgstr ""
"If they feel a neutral feeling, they understand that it’s impermanent, that "
"they’re not attached to it, and that they don’t take pleasure in it."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc21"></a>
#. VAR: Sukhañce → so sukhaṃ ce (s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "sn54.8:21.1"
msgid "Sukhañce vedanaṃ vedayati, visaṃyutto naṃ vedayati;"
msgstr "If they feel a pleasant feeling, they feel it detached."

msgctxt "sn54.8:21.2"
msgid "dukkhañce vedanaṃ vedayati, visaṃyutto naṃ vedayati;"
msgstr "If they feel a painful feeling, they feel it detached."

msgctxt "sn54.8:21.3"
msgid "adukkhamasukhañce vedanaṃ vedayati, visaṃyutto naṃ vedayati."
msgstr "If they feel a neutral feeling, they feel it detached."

msgctxt "sn54.8:21.4"
msgid ""
"So kāyapariyantikaṃ vedanaṃ vedayamāno ‘kāyapariyantikaṃ vedanaṃ vedayāmī’ti "
"pajānāti, jīvitapariyantikaṃ vedanaṃ vedayamāno ‘jīvitapariyantikaṃ vedanaṃ "
"vedayāmī’ti pajānāti, "
msgstr ""
"Feeling the end of the body approaching, they understand: ‘I feel the end of "
"the body approaching.’ Feeling the end of life approaching, they understand: "
"‘I feel the end of life approaching.’ "

msgctxt "sn54.8:21.5"
msgid ""
"‘kāyassa bhedā uddhaṃ jīvitapariyādānā idheva sabbavedayitāni "
"anabhinanditāni sītībhavissantī’ti pajānāti."
msgstr ""
"They understand: ‘When my body breaks up and my life has come to an end, "
"everything that’s felt, since I no longer take pleasure in it, will become "
"cool right here.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.320"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc22"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.8:22.1"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, telañca paṭicca, vaṭṭiñca paṭicca telappadīpo "
"jhāyeyya, "
msgstr "Suppose an oil lamp depended on oil and a wick to burn. "

msgctxt "sn54.8:22.2"
msgid "tasseva telassa ca vaṭṭiyā ca pariyādānā anāhāro nibbāyeyya;"
msgstr ""
"As the oil and the wick are used up, it would be extinguished due to lack of "
"fuel."

msgctxt "sn54.8:22.3"
msgid ""
"evameva kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kāyapariyantikaṃ vedanaṃ vedayamāno ‘"
"kāyapariyantikaṃ vedanaṃ vedayāmī’ti pajānāti, jīvitapariyantikaṃ vedanaṃ "
"vedayamāno ‘jīvitapariyantikaṃ vedanaṃ vedayāmī’ti pajānāti, "
msgstr ""
"In the same way, feeling the end of the body approaching, they understand: ‘"
"I feel the end of the body approaching.’ Feeling the end of life "
"approaching, they understand: ‘I feel the end of life approaching.’ "

msgctxt "sn54.8:22.4"
msgid ""
"‘kāyassa bhedā uddhaṃ jīvitapariyādānā idheva sabbavedayitāni "
"anabhinanditāni sītībhavissantī’ti pajānātī”ti."
msgstr ""
"They understand: ‘When my body breaks up and my life has come to an end, "
"everything that’s felt, since I no longer take pleasure in it, will become "
"cool right here.’”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn54.8:22.5"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
